    <item>
      <title>华尔街在 12 月 31 日回归之前将明确债务上限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/wall-street-is-getting-debt-ceiling-clarity-before-its-return-on-dec-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街策略师展望 12 月 31 日——目前美国债务上限的暂停何时结束——司法部得到了一些明确的消息，导致市场参与者预计国库券供应量的减少幅度较小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/wall-street-is-getting-debt-ceiling-clarity-before-its-return-on-dec-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 17:04:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
