      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:57:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在伊朗袭击后努力防止冲突蔓延</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/biden-endeavors-to-prevent-spread-of-conflict-after-iran-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登表示，周末对伊朗袭击的反应表明美国致力于维护以色列的安全，并希望防止中东冲突升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/biden-endeavors-to-prevent-spread-of-conflict-after-iran-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 16:56:38 GMT</pubDate>
